---
title: Beyond Meat®, Mixed Mushroom and Pea Cottage Pie with Cheesy Mashed Potatoes
description: This veggie take on a classic casserole combines a saucy mushroom and Beyond Meat® filling with extra-cheesy mashed potatoes. A quick broil at the end of cooking gives this cottage pie an irresistible golden crust.
